    "Example: a bash pre-hook could `defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string \"$THAW_PROFILE_NAME\"` to keep iStat Menus in sync with Thaw." : {
      "comment" : "A description of how to use environment variables in a pre-hook.",
      "localizations" : {
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Příklad: bashový pre-hook může provést příkaz `defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string \"$THAW_PROFILE_NAME\"`, aby se aplikace iStat Menus synchronizovala s Thaw."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Beispiel: Ein Bash-Pre-Hook könnte mit `defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string \"$THAW_PROFILE_NAME\"` dafür sorgen, dass iStat Menus mit Thaw synchron bleibt."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ejemplo: un pre-hook de Bash podría ejecutar `defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string «$THAW_PROFILE_NAME»` para mantener iStat Menus sincronizado con Thaw."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Exemple : un pre-hook bash pourrait exécuter \\defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string “$THAW_PROFILE_NAME”` pour garder iStat Menus synchronisé avec Thaw."
          }
        },
        "hu" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Példa: egy bash elő-hook használhatja ezt: \\defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string “$THAW_PROFILE_NAME”`, hogy az iStat Menus szinkronban maradjon a Thaw alkalmazással.`"
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Contoh: pre-hook bash bisa menjalankan `defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string \"$THAW_PROFILE_NAME\"` supaya iStat Menus tetap sinkron dengan Thaw."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Example: a bash pre-hook could `defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string \"$THAW_PROFILE_NAME\"` to keep iStat Menus in sync with Thaw."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Example: a bash pre-hook could `defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string \"$THAW_PROFILE_NAME\"` to keep iStat Menus in sync with Thaw."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "예시: bash 사전 훅 `defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string \"$THAW_PROFILE_NAME\"` 를 통해 iStat Menus와 Thaw를 동기화할 수 있습니다."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Voorbeeld: een bash pre-hook kan \\defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string “$THAW_PROFILE_NAME”` uitvoeren om iStat Menus gesynchroniseerd te houden met Thaw."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Przykład: pre-hook w bashu mógłby wykonać `defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string \"$THAW_PROFILE_NAME\"`, aby utrzymać synchronizację iStat Menus z Thaw."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Exemplo: um pré-hook do Bash poderia executar `defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string “$THAW_PROFILE_NAME”` para manter o iStat Menus sincronizado com o Thaw."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Пример: bash-скрипт pre-hook может выполнить defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string \"$THAW_PROFILE_NAME\", чтобы синхронизировать iStat Menus с Thaw."
          }
        },
        "th" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ตัวอย่าง: bash pre-hook สามารถใช้คำสั่ง `defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string \"$THAW_PROFILE_NAME\"` เพื่อให้ iStat Menus ซิงก์กับ Thaw อยู่เสมอ"
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bash pre-hook mekanizması, iStat Menus hizmetinin Thaw ile senkronize kalmasını sağlamak için defaults write com.bjango.istatmenus5 ActiveProfile -string \"$THAW_PROFILE_NAME\" komutunu çalıştırabilir."
          }
